('ACT_CLNLcf9', 'Cleanliness Management - Housekeeping & Public Area', 'USR_DMNb4b', 250000, 'https://tbh-v2.is3.cloudhost.id/IMAGE_ACTIVITY/Image-Activity-1741767472-1741767472.jpg', 1, NULL, 'https://tbh-v2.is3.cloudhost.id/SERTIF_IMAGE/Template-Certifiace-1741767473-1741767473.jpg', '2025-03-13 09:00:00', '2025-03-30 21:00:00', 1, 0, '2025-03-17 11:23:36', '<p>Program ini dirancang untuk memberikan pemahaman mendalam mengenai produk pembersih dan sanitasi dalam industri Food &amp; Beverage, sehingga Anda dapat memastikan standar kebersihan yang tinggi, menerapkan praktik sanitasi yang tepat.</p>', '<p>7,&nbsp;<br><br>Personal Hygiene</p><p><br></p><p>Bathroom &amp; Public Toilet</p><p><br></p><p>Guest Room Cleaning</p><p><br></p><p>Floor Care</p><p><br></p><p>Odor Management</p><p><br></p><p>Outdoor Facility</p><p><br></p><p>Cleaning Tools</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
('ACT_CRSC8de', 'Course Icety', 'USR_DMNb4b', 0, 'https://expo-dev.is3.cloudhost.id/IMAGE_ACTIVITY/Image-Activity-1780499711-1780499712.jpg', 1, NULL, 'https://expo-dev.is3.cloudhost.id/SERTIF_IMAGE/Template-Certifiace-1780499713-1780499713.jpg', '2026-06-03 21:54:00', '2026-07-03 21:59:00', 1, 1, '2026-06-03 22:15:13', '<p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">Lorem Ipsum</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry\'s standard dummy text ever since 1966</span></p>', '<p>3,</p><p>Food</p><p>Safety</p><p>Manajemen</p><p><br></p>', NULL, 'Course ICETy', NULL, NULL, 'Instructor', '<p>-</p>', '2026-06-03'),
('ACT_CRSP39c', 'course papago', 'USR_DMNb4b', 0, 'https://expo-dev.is3.cloudhost.id/IMAGE_ACTIVITY/Image-Activity-1777877665-1777877665.jpg', 1, NULL, 'https://expo-dev.is3.cloudhost.id/SERTIF_IMAGE/Template-Certifiace-1777877667-1777877667.jpg', '2026-05-04 13:50:00', '2026-07-04 13:51:00', 1, 1, '2026-05-04 15:24:13', '<p>asdad</p>', '<p>2,</p><p>animasi</p><p>poster</p>', NULL, 'papgo', NULL, NULL, '-', '<p>course papagooo</p>', '2026-05-04'),
('ACT_CRSVc15', 'Course Val 2', 'USR_DMNb4b', 120000, 'https://expo-dev.is3.cloudhost.id/IMAGE_ACTIVITY/Image-Activity-1774615592-1774615592.jpg', 1, NULL, 'https://expo-dev.is3.cloudhost.id/SERTIF_IMAGE/Template-Certifiace-1774615594-1774615594.jpg', '2026-03-27 19:43:00', '2026-03-31 19:43:00', 0, 1, '2026-03-27 19:46:47', '<p>Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry\'s standard dummy text ever since the 1500s, when an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a type specimen book. It has survived not only five centuries, but also the leap into electronic typesetting, remaining essentially unchanged. It was popularised in the 1960s with the release of Letraset sheets containing Lorem Ipsum passages, and more recently with desktop publishing software like Aldus PageMaker including versions of Lorem Ipsum.</p>', '<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.</p><p>Sed eu elit gravida, iaculis velit non, ultrices tortor.</p><p>Vivamus commodo nunc a sem vulputate, nec ornare augue porttitor.</p><p>Aliquam finibus ligula blandit diam egestas pellentesque a vitae augue.</p><p>Cras id massa sit amet est hendrerit faucibus.</p>', NULL, 'Certificate of Completion Vals', NULL, NULL, 'joinprogram', '<p>Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry\'s standard dummy text ever since the 1500s, when an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a type specimen book. It has survived not only five centuries, but also the leap into electronic typesetting, remaining essentially unchanged. It was popularised in the 1960s with the release of Letraset sheets containing Lorem Ipsum passages, and more recently with desktop publishing software like Aldus PageMaker including versions of Lorem Ipsum.</p><p><br></p>', '2026-03-27'),
('ACT_DBLL158', 'Adobe Illustrator', 'USR_DMNb4b', 378000, 'https://icety-data.is3.cloudhost.id/IMAGE_ACTIVITY/Image-Activity-1755590601-1755590601.jpg', 1, NULL, 'https://icety-data.is3.cloudhost.id/SERTIF_IMAGE/Template-Certifiace-1755590601-1755590601.jpg', '2025-08-19 14:59:00', '2027-08-19 23:59:00', 1, 1, '2025-08-27 16:21:04', '<p>Peserta yang menyelesaikan kursus ini dinyatakan telah menguasai keterampilan dasar hingga menengah dalam menggunakan Adobe Illustrator CS6 untuk desain vektor. Dengan sertifikat ini, peserta memiliki bukti kompetensi dalam pembuatan logo, ilustrasi karakter, serta desain kreatif berbasis vektor.</p>', '<p>12,</p><p>Tools Overview</p><p>Vectorization Techniques</p><p>Basic Shape &amp; Path Editing</p><p>Typography in Illustrator</p><p>Coloring &amp; Gradients</p><p>Logo Design Fundamentals</p><p>Advanced Logo Creation</p><p>Character Design Basics</p><p>Character Design Advanced</p><p>Illustration Project</p><p>Final Project – Logo/Character</p><p>Portfolio Presentation &amp; Review</p>', '2025-08-28 03:24:33', 'Certificate of Completion in Adobe Illustrator CS6', NULL, NULL, 'Jaya, Alief, Karin', '<p>-</p>', NULL),
('ACT_DBLLdae', 'Illustrator Coursee2e21', 'USR_DMNb4b', 500000, 'https://icety-data.is3.cloudhost.id/IMAGE_ACTIVITY/Image-Activity-1761272707-1761272707.jpg', 1, NULL, 'https://icety-data.is3.cloudhost.id/SERTIF_IMAGE/Sertificate-Template-1761361742-1761361742.jpg', '2025-08-19 22:18:00', '2027-08-31 22:18:00', 1, 1, '2026-04-01 11:14:49', '<p>Sertifikat ini membuktikan kompetensi Anda dalam merancang dan mengimplementasikan karya visual yang menarik serta fungsional, dengan pendekatan berbasis riset untuk menghasilkan pengalaman desain yang optimal.</p>', '<p>6,</p><p>Introduction to Adobe Illustrator &amp; Basic Tools</p><p>Coloring Techniques and Gradient Applications</p><p>Vectorization Fundamentals</p><p>Logo Design: Logotype and Logogram Creation</p><p>Poster &amp; Layout Design</p><p>Sketching and Developing Original Character Designs</p>', NULL, 'Illustrator Course', NULL, NULL, 'joinprogram', '<p style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; color: rgb(119, 131, 143); font-family: Jost, sans-serif; line-height: 30px; font-size: 16px;\">Ada 4 Instruktur pada Illustrator Course yaitu;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; color: rgb(119, 131, 143); font-family: Jost, sans-serif; line-height: 30px; font-size: 16px;\">Kak Jaya,&nbsp; Kak Dimas Cahyo, Kak Karin dan Kak Alief</p>', '2026-03-31'),
('ACT_DBPH4d0', 'Desain Grafis edit admin', 'USR_JNPR65e', 378000, 'https://icety-data.is3.cloudhost.id/IMAGE_ACTIVITY/Image-Activity-1761216054-1761216054.jpg', 1, NULL, 'https://icety-data.is3.cloudhost.id/SERTIF_IMAGE/Sertificate-Template-1761362009-1761362009.jpg', '2025-08-19 10:51:00', '2027-08-19 23:59:00', 1, 1, '2026-04-01 11:26:24', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(83, 83, 95);\">Peserta dinyatakan telah menguasai keterampilan dasar hingga menengah dalam penggunaan </span><span data-start=\"420\" data-end=\"439\" style=\"color: rgb(83, 83, 95);\">Adobe Photoshop</span><span style=\"color: rgb(83, 83, 95);\"> untuk kebutuhan </span><span data-start=\"456\" data-end=\"507\" style=\"color: rgb(83, 83, 95);\">pengolahan gambar dan desain grafis profesional.</span></p>', '<p>6,</p><p>Introduction to Basic Tools</p><p>Typography, Photo Editing &amp; Color Grading</p><p>Photography Editing Techniques</p><p>Applying Dramatic Effects &amp; Surreal Art Concepts</p><p>Photo Manipulation</p><p>AI Applications for Design &amp; Digital Collage</p>', NULL, 'Design Grafis Course', NULL, NULL, 'joinprogram', '<p style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; color: rgb(119, 131, 143); line-height: 30px; font-family: Jost, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Ada 3 Instruktur pada Design Grafis Course yaitu;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; color: rgb(119, 131, 143); line-height: 30px; font-family: Jost, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Kak Destri, Kak Aditya, dan Kak Alief</p>', '2026-04-01'),
('ACT_DBPR2b1', 'Editing Video', 'USR_DMNb4b', 378000, 'https://icety-data.is3.cloudhost.id/IMAGE_ACTIVITY/Image-Activity-1761204248-1761204248.jpg', 1, NULL, 'https://icety-data.is3.cloudhost.id/SERTIF_IMAGE/Sertificate-Template-1761364135-1761364135.jpg', '2025-08-19 23:59:00', '2027-08-19 23:59:00', 1, 1, '2025-10-25 10:48:55', '<p>Peserta yang menyelesaikan kursus ini dinyatakan telah menguasai keterampilan editing video menggunakan Adobe Premiere Pro mulai dari dasar hingga menengah. Sertifikat ini menjadi bukti kompetensi dalam mengolah video secara profesional, mencakup audio, transisi, color grading, hingga hasil akhir siap tayang.</p>', '<p>12,</p><p>Workspace Overview</p><p>Project Setup &amp; File Management</p><p>Basic Editing: Cutting &amp; Trimming</p><p>Timeline &amp; Sequence Mastery</p><p>Working with Audio: Editing &amp; Mixing</p><p>Transitions &amp; Basic Effects</p><p>Titles &amp; Motion Graphics Basics</p><p>Color Correction &amp; Adjustment Layers</p><p>Advanced Color Grading</p><p>Green Screen &amp; Keying Techniques</p><p>Final Project: Short Video Editing</p><p>Exporting, Rendering &amp; Portfolio Review</p>', '2025-10-25 04:25:32', 'Certificate of Completion in Adobe Premiere Pro', NULL, NULL, 'joinprogram', '<p>-</p>', NULL),
('ACT_DN2a2', 'daun', 'USR_DMNb4b', 0, 'https://expo-dev.is3.cloudhost.id/IMAGE_ACTIVITY/Image-Activity-1734417330-1734417330.png', 2, 'UU', 'https://expo-dev.is3.cloudhost.id/SERTIF_IMAGE/Template-Certifiace-1732769805-1732769805.jpg', '2024-12-18 11:54:00', '2024-12-19 11:54:00', 1, 0, '2024-12-18 12:16:46', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
('ACT_DSNX1db', 'Desain UI/UX Versi Website', 'USR_JNPR65e', 378000, 'https://icety-data.is3.cloudhost.id/IMAGE_ACTIVITY/Image-Activity-1759651950-1759651950.jpg', 1, NULL, 'https://icety-data.is3.cloudhost.id/SERTIF_IMAGE/Template-Certifiace-1759651951-1759651951.jpg', '2025-10-05 15:01:00', '2026-08-31 15:01:00', 1, 1, '2025-10-25 09:38:52', '<p>Sertifikat ini membuktikan kompetensi anda dalam merancang antarmuka website yang menarik secara visual sekaligus memberikan pengalaman yang optimal melalui pendekatan berbasis riset.</p>', '<p>8,</p><p>Pengenalan UI/UX &amp; Desain Digital</p><p>Prinsip Dasar Desain Visual &amp; Layout Grid</p><p>User Research &amp; Persona</p><p>Wireframing Dasar</p><p>Warna &amp; Tipografi</p><p>Komponen UI &amp; Design System</p><p>Desain Ikon &amp; Ilustrasi </p><p>Spacing &amp; Alignment</p>', NULL, 'UI/UX website Design', NULL, NULL, 'joinprogram', '<p>Ada 3 Instruktur pada materi Desain UI/UX yaitu;</p><p>Kak Adam Abdillah,&nbsp; Kak Teguh Maulana dan Kak Laksamana Nala</p><div><br></div>', NULL),
('ACT_DSNX54e', 'Desain UI/UX Versi Website', 'USR_DMNb4b', 378000, 'https://icety-data.is3.cloudhost.id/IMAGE_ACTIVITY/Image-Activity-1755760352-1755760352.jpg', 1, NULL, 'https://icety-data.is3.cloudhost.id/SERTIF_IMAGE/Template-Certifiace-1755760356-1755760356.jpg', '2025-08-19 14:07:00', '2027-08-17 23:59:00', 1, 1, '2025-10-05 14:17:19', '<p>Peserta yang menyelesaikan kursus ini dinyatakan telah menguasai prinsip dasar hingga menengah dalam UI/UX Website Design. Sertifikat ini membuktikan kompetensi dalam merancang antarmuka website yang menarik secara visual sekaligus memberikan pengalaman pengguna yang optimal melalui pendekatan berbasis riset.</p>', '<p>12,</p><p>Introduction to UI/UX Design &amp; Design Thinking</p><p>Understanding User Needs &amp; Research Methods</p><p>Creating User Persona &amp; User Journey Mapping</p><p>Website Information Architecture &amp; Navigation Flow</p><p>Wireframing Fundamentals</p><p>Low-Fidelity Prototyping</p>', '2025-10-05 08:14:01', 'Certificate of Completion in UI/UX Website Design', NULL, NULL, 'Adam Abdillah, Teguh Maulana, Laksamana Nala', '<p>-</p>', NULL),
('ACT_DSNX774', 'Desain UI/UX Versi Website', 'USR_JNPR65e', 378000, 'https://icety-data.is3.cloudhost.id/IMAGE_ACTIVITY/Image-Activity-1759650824-1759650824.jpg', 1, NULL, 'https://icety-data.is3.cloudhost.id/SERTIF_IMAGE/Template-Certifiace-1759650827-1759650827.jpg', '2025-10-05 14:25:00', '2026-08-05 14:25:00', 0, 1, '2025-10-05 14:53:47', '<p>Sertifikat ini membuktikan kompetensi anda dalam merancang antarmuka website yang menarik secara visual sekaligus memberikan pengalaman yang optimal melalui pendekatan berbasis riset.</p>', '<p>12,</p><p>Pengenalan UI/UX &amp; Desain Digital</p><p>Prinsip Dasar Desain Visual, Layout Grid &amp; Struktur Website</p><p>User Research &amp; Persona</p><p>Wireframing Dasar</p><p>Warna &amp; Tipografi</p><p>Komponen UI &amp; Design System</p><p>Desain Ikon, Ilustrasi spacing &amp; Alignment</p>', '2025-10-05 07:58:18', 'UI/UX website Design', NULL, NULL, 'joinprogram', '<p>Ada 3 Instruktur pada materi Desain UI/UX yaitu;</p><p>Kak Adam Abdillah,&nbsp; Kak Teguh Maulana dan Kak Laksamana Nala</p>', NULL),
('ACT_DTNGeb8', 'Editing Video Course', 'USR_JNPR65e', 378000, 'https://icety-data.is3.cloudhost.id/IMAGE_ACTIVITY/Image-Activity-1761365643-1761365643.jpg', 1, NULL, 'https://icety-data.is3.cloudhost.id/SERTIF_IMAGE/Template-Certifiace-1761365646-1761365646.jpg', '2025-10-20 10:53:00', '2027-08-25 10:53:00', 1, 1, '2025-10-25 11:14:06', '<p>Sertifikat ini menegaskan kemampuan Anda dalam mengedit dan memproduksi video kreatif yang menarik secara visual serta efektif dalam menyampaikan pesan.</p>', '<p>6,</p><p>Introduction to Adobe Premiere &amp; Basic Tools</p><p><br></p>', NULL, 'Editing Video Course', NULL, NULL, 'joinprogram', '<p>Instruktur Pada Course Editing Video yaitu:</p><p>Kak Alief dan Kak Destri</p>', NULL),
('ACT_FDSF96d', 'Food Safety Management Course - iClean+ Internal', 'USR_DMNb4b', 500000, 'https://tbh-v2.is3.cloudhost.id/IMAGE_ACTIVITY/Image-Activity-1740036307-1740036307.png', 1, NULL, 'https://tbh-v2.is3.cloudhost.id/SERTIF_IMAGE/Template-Certifiace-1740036307-1740036307.jpg', '2025-02-20 14:16:00', '2028-12-31 14:17:00', 1, 0, '2025-09-15 14:18:45', '<p>Dengan mengikuti FSMC ini dan mendapatkan certificate maka anda telah siap menjadi professional di industri culinary.</p>', '<ul><li>8,&nbsp;</li><li><br></li><li>Preventing Foodborne Illness</li><li>Personal Hygiene and Conduct</li><li>Time and Temperature Control</li><li>Food Procurement and Receiving</li><li>Food Storage Management</li><li>Safe Food Preparation</li><li>Food Service and Handling</li><li>Sanitation and Pest Control</li></ul>', NULL, 'FSMC', NULL, NULL, '-', NULL, NULL),
('ACT_FDSFc0d', 'Food Safety Management Course', 'USR_DMNb4b', 500000, 'https://tbh-v2.is3.cloudhost.id/IMAGE_ACTIVITY/Image-Activity-1741732077-1741732077.jpg', 1, NULL, 'https://tbh-v2.is3.cloudhost.id/SERTIF_IMAGE/Template-Certifiace-1741732077-1741732077.jpg', '2025-03-13 01:00:00', '2025-03-30 21:00:00', 1, 1, '2025-03-13 10:30:31', '<p>Kursus ini membahas dasar-dasar cleaning dan sanitasi, termasuk langkah-langkah pembersihan yang benar serta faktor pendukungnya seperti air dan deterjen. Selain itu, peserta juga akan mendapatkan wawasan mengenai sanitasi dan mikroorganisme untuk meningkatkan efektivitas kebersihan.</p>', '<p>3,<br>Cleaning Factors</p><p>Cleaning vs Sanitation</p><p>Detergency</p><p><br></p>', '2025-03-11 22:30:23', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
('ACT_FDSFd4e', 'Food Safety Management Course - AII & iClean+ Collaboration', 'USR_DMNb4b', 500000, 'https://tbh-v2.is3.cloudhost.id/IMAGE_ACTIVITY/Image-Activity-1740036307-1740036307.png', 1, NULL, 'https://tbh-v2.is3.cloudhost.id/SERTIF_IMAGE/Sertificate-Template-1742556030-1742556030.jpg', '2025-02-20 14:16:00', '2026-12-20 14:17:00', 1, 0, '2026-01-09 16:14:36', '<p>Dengan mengikuti FSM/HACCP Course ini dan mendapatkan certificate maka anda telah siap menjadi professional di industri culinary.</p>', '<p>8,</p><p>Preventing Foodborne Illness</p><p>Personal Hygiene and Conduct</p><p>Time and Temperature Control</p><p>Food Procurement and Receiving</p><p>Food Storage Management</p><p>Safe Food Preparation</p><p>Food Service and Handling</p><p>Sanitation and Pest Control</p>', NULL, 'Food Safety Management / HACCP Course', NULL, NULL, '-', NULL, NULL),
