(1, 'https://expo-dev.is3.cloudhost.id/IMAGE_ABOUT/Image-About-1764215592-1764215592.jpg', 'PJ Global School, founded in 2007, delivers international-standard education for Indonesian and expatriate students, empowering them with life skills and global competencies. As part of the ICETy Digital Learning Network, the school integrates future-ready learning, digital certifications, and international exposure programs, providing students access to a wider global education ecosystem. Together, PJ Global School and ICETy aim to shape creative, capable, and globally minded young learners.');
